dct_title_s: Vilayet Constantinople : Dépendences en Turquie d'Asie
dct_description_sm: Prime meridian is Paris. Map shows administrative boundaries; railroads, roads; and forests. Vilayet de Constantinople was a first level administrative division vilayet  [province] of the Ottoman Empire. Covers 1. Ville de Constantinople : VIIIme Cercle municipal: Kandlidja -- IXme : Scutari (Uskudar) -- Xme : Cadikkeu. 2. Cinq cazas : 1.Iles de Princes -- 2 Guèbzè --3. Béicos --4. Kartal -- Chilé. Original map is filed in the Map/Geospatial Center, a map reproduction is attached to companion volume.
